title: Possibly fixed voson-lab/SocialMediaLab#15
body:
voson-lab/SocialMediaLab#15 is not a bug but a "feature". It should pop-up a useful error message to flag the error is due to empty comment in the given `VideoIDs`.

Also added the unit test framework to make sure it will not resurface in future update.

title: Convert the original .Rd files into Roxygen2 comments.
body: Documentation and NAMESPACE can now be (re-)generated by devtools::document()

title: Created three verb functions to be used with magrittr %>% operator and addressed concerns from pull request #3
body:
Similar to the previous pull request but implemented the Ego network related functions.
All added functions have .Rd created (with roxygen2).

``` r
require(roxygen2)
roxygenise("./SocialMediaLab", roclets = c("rd"))
```

title: Created three verb functions to be used with magrittr %>% operators
body:
I have tested the Authenticate, Collect, Create, LoadCredential, SaveCredential functions with Youtube, Facebook and Twitter but not Instagram. I cannot create an App that can access to the public endpoints. It should work..... should.... 

Magrittr has been added as Suggests, maybe should put it as Imports.

I basically touch nothing on the previous code except CollectDataFacebook.R and CollectDataInstagram.R. It will not affect the previous user experience that rely on side effect.

I will create the .Rd if this pull request is accepted.
